    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it! It's in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that looks and feels brand new, you've found it! Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
