    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true time-capsule vehicle. Meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, the exterior retains its original deep luster with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather is supple and free of any creasing, and the original factory scent persists. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates with the precision of the day it was manufactured. This vehicle has never seen rain, boasts a comprehensive service history from the original dealership, and has been treated as a collector's piece rather than a daily driver. If you are seeking perfection, this is it.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
